metadata.name: Dancing Baby by Yuuki Morita
metadata.description:
„This dancing baby represents the cry of those of us who live in the chaos of modern times. We inherently wish to show more of our various expressions, but society refuses to let us do so.
This baby's expressionless face seems to be the face of our inability to show our true face even if we wanted to. The various facial expressions on the head of this baby, dancing around with a straight face, represent the true inner workings of our hearts.“ - Yuuki Morita
